{"title":"夏天","authors":["段和平"],"dates":[{"year":1988,"month":9,"day":5}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"夏天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"段和平"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仿佛走在时光的尽头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眩目的太阳烧焦了正午。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手臂如双浆划动季节，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"头顶是卷缩的树叶。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在无风的白天和夜晚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"感觉奔走于七月流火。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"即使面对宁静的湖泊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也无法熄灭灼人的火焰。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走过灌浆的夏日，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是收获的金秋。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}